*ItHotSQ* is a sprawling old-school hexcrawl using PBtA mechanics (2d6 + stat, loose structure of Moves). It&#39;s a 56-page paperback or PDF designed for one player and one GM. Packaged with character sheet and three full-color maps.

[Here&#39;s an actual play on Twitch](https://www.twitch.tv/videos/941248349).

[And here&#39;s the website](https://www.trailofdice.com/in-the-hollow-of-the-spider-queen.html).

